    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, without hyperbole, the finest example of this model currently on the market. Meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free from stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather surfaces are supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the original floor mats are pristine. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives with the tight, responsive precision of a brand-new vehicle. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a truly preserved piece of automotive excellence.",
